Package: pipewelder
Title: Public Data Retrieval Pipelines for R
Version: 0.1.4
Authors@R: 
    person("Temistocles", "Valdes", , "valdestr@leg3.net", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides helper functions for retrieving and standardizing public data from sources such as BLS, FRED, and CDC. The package supports reproducible analytical workflows by wrapping source-specific API and parsing logic in reusable R functions.
